articles.title: Oceanography, Seafloor Mapping and Satellite Combine to Map World's Strongest Current - AZoCleantech
articles.description: From space to the seafloor, an Australian and international research voyage has mapped a highly energetic "hotspot" in the world’s strongest current simultaneously by ship and satellite, and uncovered an underwater mountain range.
